          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Conclusions: the differential cross section for the",
                " Li-7(D,A) reaction at 90 degrees was determined by",
                "relatively simple thick target method, using state",
                "detectors. The energy dependance of the cross section",
                "was found to agree with that for the formation of the",
                "compound nucleus, in the energy range 175-300 KeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
